{"type":"message","id":"2b2c7bda","parentId":"66fd2ded","timestamp":"2026-03-24T05:40:18.980Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the full picture. Let me summarize the pulse results:\n\n1. The pulse detected 1 proposed mutation (TIC Experiment)\n2. It created a Python script for the TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment\n3. The experiment aims to test the hypothesis that \"causal structure = invariant structure\"\n4. Success criteria: >70% invariant/variant classification accuracy, >60% next-pulse prediction\n5. The script was written to logs/\n\nLet me give a concise summary.","thinkingSignature":"a90e1c32c834c8af92a21aa9f45b1744d32dbac7a3761abafec790a8fa220248"},{"type":"text","text":"**Sandbox Pulse — 2026-03-24 01:39 AM**\n\n✅ **Cycle complete.** No errors.\n\n---\n\n**Key events this pulse:**\n\n- **1 mutation proposed** — A new Python experiment file (`TIC_experiment.py`) was created in the sandbox's `logs/` directory\n- The script implements the **Temporal Invariance Compression (TIC) experiment** — testing the hypothesis that *causal structure = invariant structure*\n- Success targets: >70% invariant/variant classification accuracy, >60% next-pulse prediction accuracy\n\n**Invariant/variant approach:**\n- Extracts content blocks from pulse logs\n- Classifies content appearing in ≥50% of pulses as invariant\n- Tests classification accuracy on held-out test pulses\n- Attempts to predict next-pulse content from invariant patterns\n\n**Current state:** The TIC experiment is staged and ready to run against the accumulated pulse logs. The next pulse will likely execute and evaluate it."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3375,"output":299,"cacheRead":11954,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15628,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774330805237}}
